As noted in Sect. 2, we follow the basic formation of our stochastic SEIRS model as in Méndez et al. (2012). In particular, the model we consider here captures only the stochastic nature of the transmission function with the Weiner process explicitly in the formation of the function \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
